Label: Date of Collection
Lookup/Notes:
Must be one of the following:
1.   A valid date in the form of MM/DD/YYYY
2.   If the date is unknown, then code:   99/99/9999

For Tissue Source of Autopsy, Date of Collection should be equal to or within 5 days after death.

Label: Age at Date of Collection (Years)
Lookup/Notes:
Must be one of the following:
1.   A valid age between 000 and 125
2.   If Age is unknown, then code 999
